{
  "id": "RAW_b6ba4e",
  "title": "居然说我的设计不够精致！哼，那我只好放大招了",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyMjgzNDgzOQ==&mid=2247530792&idx=1&sn=c381296e0d77ceb24ee8fbea8478882e",
  "date": "2025-05-29 00:20:00",
  "author": "菜心设计铺",
  "siteName": "体验进阶",
  "content": "\n \n \n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"m9mjxibd1iuz\">\n   <span data-metadata=\"<!--(figmeta)eyJmaWxlS2V5IjoiMGFqZ0ZPblJzTXVBMnBQQkZxSUZZaCIsInBhc3RlSUQiOjUxMDE1MTQ5MiwiZGF0YVR5cGUiOiJzY2VuZSJ9Cg==(/figmeta)-->\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-size: 15px\"></span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"></span><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">“这个设计感觉不够精致啊...”——作为新人设计师，你是否也经常听到这样的反馈？明明熬夜改了几十稿，却总被说“差点意思”；照着大厂设计做，却显得生硬呆板。</span></span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n   <span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">其实，90%的“粗糙感”都来自容易被忽略的细节。今天我们拆解案例，教你用最小修改成本实现设计质感的飞跃。无需复杂技巧，看完立刻能用！</span></span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n   <span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;font-size: 15px;\"><span data-metadata=\"<!--(figmeta)eyJmaWxlS2V5IjoiMGFqZ0ZPblJzTXVBMnBQQkZxSUZZaCIsInBhc3RlSUQiOjkwNDM2NzEyMSwiZGF0YVR5cGUiOiJzY2VuZSJ9Cg==(/figmeta)-->\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"></span><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;font-size: 24px;\" mpa-font-style=\"m9mjxm5m1sul\" data-mpa-action-id=\"m9mjxm61our\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">直接上干货</span></span></span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n   <span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span data-metadata=\"<!--(figmeta)eyJmaWxlS2V5IjoiMGFqZ0ZPblJzTXVBMnBQQkZxSUZZaCIsInBhc3RlSUQiOjEzODQ1ODAyMDQsImRhdGFUeXBlIjoic2NlbmUifQo=(/figmeta)-->\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"></span><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;font-size: 20px;\" mpa-font-style=\"m9mjxq6e1ycn\" data-mpa-action-id=\"m9mjxq6t2008\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">1.图标精度</span></span></span></span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n   <span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span data-metadata=\"<!--(figmeta)eyJmaWxlS2V5IjoiMGFqZ0ZPblJzTXVBMnBQQkZxSUZZaCIsInBhc3RlSUQiOjEyOTAyMjY3NjEsImRhdGFUeXBlIjoic2NlbmUifQo=(/figmeta)-->\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"></span><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">这是不是你画的图标？造型基本OK，加了渐变，加了装饰元素，也加了描边；但是依然差点意思</span></span></span></span></span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/51c3afd7-c949-4910-8473-2349fddb0a00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5383290267011197\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1161\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100044225\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/51c3afd7-c949-4910-8473-2349fddb0a00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n   <span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span data-metadata=\"<!--(figmeta)eyJmaWxlS2V5IjoiMGFqZ0ZPblJzTXVBMnBQQkZxSUZZaCIsInBhc3RlSUQiOjk2OTExNzYzOCwiZGF0YVR5cGUiOiJzY2VuZSJ9Cg==(/figmeta)-->\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"></span><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">有同学就会疑惑了，都做到这个份上了，还不算精致吗？先来看看对比图：</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3778f857-f65d-41af-cc7a-997068cf6500/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5383290267011197\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1161\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100044226\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3778f857-f65d-41af-cc7a-997068cf6500/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n   <span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span data-metadata=\"<!--(figmeta)eyJmaWxlS2V5IjoiMGFqZ0ZPblJzTXVBMnBQQkZxSUZZaCIsInBhc3RlSUQiOjgxMjg4NzIyNywiZGF0YVR5cGUiOiJzY2VuZSJ9Cg==(/figmeta)-->\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"></span><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">有了一些细微的调整后是不是好很多，步骤如下 ⬇️</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n   <span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span data-metadata=\"<!--(figmeta)eyJmaWxlS2V5IjoiMGFqZ0ZPblJzTXVBMnBQQkZxSUZZaCIsInBhc3RlSUQiOjY2NTUyNDk2MSwiZGF0YVR5cGUiOiJzY2VuZSJ9Cg==(/figmeta)-->\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"></span><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"m9mjxweef56\" style=\"font-size: 17px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"m9mjxwem1vh6\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">① 造型调整：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">原图标造型没有什么太大的问题，但后面的文件夹凸起部分有点过多，也和下方矩形衔接的不是很自然：</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/60c31b37-628e-4cb8-a5e4-05fad214e100/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5581395348837209\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1161\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100044227\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/60c31b37-628e-4cb8-a5e4-05fad214e100/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n   <span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span data-metadata=\"<!--(figmeta)eyJmaWxlS2V5IjoiMGFqZ0ZPblJzTXVBMnBQQkZxSUZZaCIsInBhc3RlSUQiOjE4NDUxOTc4MywiZGF0YVR5cGUiOiJzY2VuZSJ9Cg==(/figmeta)-->\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"></span><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"m9mjy0t814sp\" style=\"font-size: 17px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"m9mjy0tg6hp\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">② &nbsp;颜色调整：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">原图标颜色有点显脏，查看前方的矩形，发现问题出在深色的选择上，它的‌亮度往下了，所以会显脏；</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">那么首先就去调整它的亮度到100。然后再细微调整饱和度和色相（其他显脏的部分同理）：</span></span></span></span></span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ff865925-5912-495f-2056-e73e32e44500/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5581395348837209\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1161\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100044228\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ff865925-5912-495f-2056-e73e32e44500/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/58086ce6-f404-4406-4dc3-f31a38915900/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5167958656330749\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1161\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100044229\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/58086ce6-f404-4406-4dc3-f31a38915900/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n   <span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span data-metadata=\"<!--(figmeta)eyJmaWxlS2V5IjoiMGFqZ0ZPblJzTXVBMnBQQkZxSUZZaCIsInBhc3RlSUQiOjQ0MzE2NzYyMCwiZGF0YVR5cGUiOiJzY2VuZSJ9Cg==(/figmeta)-->\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"></span><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"m9mjy5fp24p7\" style=\"font-size: 17px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"m9mjy5fqi2l\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">③ 单元素细节：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">可以看到图标中有2个装饰性元素，前面的爱心和中间夹着的文件；我们也需要对它们进行进一步的细化，而不是直接一个纯色块儿放上就可以了。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n   <span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span data-metadata=\"<!--(figmeta)eyJmaWxlS2V5IjoiMGFqZ0ZPblJzTXVBMnBQQkZxSUZZaCIsInBhc3RlSUQiOjExMDc5MDU4NzEsImRhdGFUeXBlIjoic2NlbmUifQo=(/figmeta)-->\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"></span><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">先看爱心，简单的调整一下爱心的颜色，再加一个投影就能得到不错的效果：</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f6bf9b91-a934-4362-3c66-4d5917b8cb00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5167958656330749\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1161\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100044230\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f6bf9b91-a934-4362-3c66-4d5917b8cb00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n   <span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span data-metadata=\"<!--(figmeta)eyJmaWxlS2V5IjoiMGFqZ0ZPblJzTXVBMnBQQkZxSUZZaCIsInBhc3RlSUQiOjE3Mjk1NTA4NzAsImRhdGFUeXBlIjoic2NlbmUifQo=(/figmeta)-->\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"></span><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">中间夹着的文件也是同样的手法来优化；正着摆放会稍微有点死板，我们可以尝试变换角度使其倾斜，这样图标会更加生动：</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9b2df5a1-925a-4e7c-32d6-663e65e6c300/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5167958656330749\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1161\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100044231\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9b2df5a1-925a-4e7c-32d6-663e65e6c300/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n   <span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span data-metadata=\"<!--(figmeta)eyJmaWxlS2V5IjoiMGFqZ0ZPblJzTXVBMnBQQkZxSUZZaCIsInBhc3RlSUQiOjE0MTA3MDk2MTUsImRhdGFUeXBlIjoic2NlbmUifQo=(/figmeta)-->\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"></span><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"m9mjya7f14yd\" style=\"font-size: 17px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"m9mjya7hwdq\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">④ 整体细节再调整：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">看看整体效果，发现文件夹前方的矩形需要一点厚度，原图标其实也有加，但是太细了不明显；那我们就直接加大描边数值即可：</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c4007125-11f9-4650-133a-01d0e5bbda00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5167958656330749\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1161\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100044232\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c4007125-11f9-4650-133a-01d0e5bbda00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n   <span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span data-metadata=\"<!--(figmeta)eyJmaWxlS2V5IjoiMGFqZ0ZPblJzT